FBIS4-11504 "drlat082_r_94011" FBIS-LAT-94-082 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 Peru Ecuador's Paredes Stops Over On Way Back From Rio Ecuador's Paredes Stops Over On Way Back From Rio PY2604193994 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network in Spanish 1800 GMT 26 Apr 94 PY2604193994 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network Spanish BFN [Relay from Jorge Chaves International Airport by Walter Samuel Neira] [Text] Ecuadoran Foreign Minister Diego Paredes has left for his country after spending the night in Peru. Paredes was on his way back from a meeting of Latin American foreign ministers with European representatives in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, last weekend. The Ecuadoran minister, who avoided the media before leaving, was taken in an official vehicle straight to the foot of the aircraft steps.
